{"prompt": "Generate a website for a e-commerce store. The website should be elegant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elegant Red Boutique</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #a00000;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #555;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #a00000;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .product-card {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .product-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .product-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        }\n        .product-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        .product-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #a00000;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n        }\n        .product-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        .price {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #444;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        .buy-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px 0;\n            background-color: #a00000;\n            color: #fff;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            text-align: center;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .buy-button:hover {\n            background-color: #800000;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #eee;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Elegant Red Boutique</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#home\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n    <main id=\"home\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/D3D3D3/000000?text=Product+1\" alt=\"Elegant Scarf\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Silk Embrace Scarf</h3>\n                    <p>Luxurious pure silk scarf with intricate red floral patterns. Perfect for adding a touch of sophistication.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$75.00</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/D3D3D3/000000?text=Product+2\" alt=\"Leather Handbag\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Leather Tote</h3>\n                    <p>Handcrafted genuine leather tote in a deep crimson hue. Spacious and stylish for everyday use.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$180.00</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/D3D3D3/000000?text=Product+3\" alt=\"Velvet Dress\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Ruby Velvet Dress</h3>\n                    <p>Sumptuous velvet dress designed for evening elegance. Features a flattering silhouette and a subtle sheen.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$150.00</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/D3D3D3/000000?text=Product+4\" alt=\"Gold Necklace\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Garnet Pendant Necklace</h3>\n                    <p>Delicate gold-plated necklace with a stunning red garnet pendant. A timeless piece to cherish.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$95.00</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n    <section id=\"about\" style=\"text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px; background-color: #f0f0f0;\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p style=\"max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">\n            Welcome to Elegant Red Boutique, where passion meets style. We curate a collection of exquisite fashion pieces designed to make you feel confident and beautiful. From luxurious accessories to statement apparel, our focus is on quality, elegance, and a touch of passionate red.\n        </p>\n    </section>\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elegant Red Boutique. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us: info@elegantred.com</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}